abstract_ssm: Hour-long rehearsal of the Police. Tenth Planet Productions 3/10/03. Some pre-concert conversation with Sting. Conversations between the band members. Rehearsal of "Roxanne" with Sting speaking the vocals. "Message in a Bottle" rehearsal. Some talking between the band afterwards.
